sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway / Envoy<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant vLLMMetrics as vLLM Pods (Metrics)<br/>HTTP scraping
    participant vLLMZMQ as vLLM Pods (KV Events)<br/>5556/TCP ZMQ
    participant Tokenizer as UDS Tokenizer<br/>Unix Domain Socket
    participant Sidecar as P/D Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/S
    participant Prefiller as Prefiller Pod<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Decoder as Decoder Pod<br/>8001/TCP HTTP/S

    Note over EPP,K8sAPI: Initialization & Continuous Watch
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pod, InferenceObjective,<br/>InferenceModelRewrite CRs (SA token auth)
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: CR events (add/update/delete)
    EPP->>vLLMMetrics: Periodic: Scrape Prometheus metrics<br/>(queue depth, KV cache %, LoRA info)
    vLLMMetrics-->>EPP: Metrics response
    EPP->>vLLMZMQ: Subscribe: KV cache block events<br/>(ZMQ PUB/SUB, no auth)
    vLLMZMQ-->>EPP: Real-time KV cache events

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Standard Inference Request Routing
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80 (no auth)
    Gateway->>EPP: ext_proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC streaming (9002/TCP)
    EPP->>Tokenizer: Tokenize prompt<br/>(gRPC over UDS)
    Tokenizer-->>EPP: Token IDs
    Note over EPP: Scheduling Pipeline:<br/>1. Filters (admission, model match)<br/>2. Scorers (prefix cache, load, KV util)<br/>3. Picker (max score)
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>Set target-pod header
    Gateway->>Decoder: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/8000

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated P/D Inference
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Gateway->>EPP: ext_proc ProcessingRequest
    Note over EPP: Scheduling: Select prefill + decode pods<br/>Set x-prefill-host, x-decode-host headers
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>(target = decode pod with sidecar)
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward to decode pod sidecar<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP
    Sidecar->>Prefiller: Forward prefill request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (SSRF validated)
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill response + KV cache params
    Note over Sidecar: KV Cache Transfer<br/>(NIXL V2 / Shared Storage / SGLang)
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Decode request with KV params<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8001/TCP
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: Streamed response
    Gateway-->>Client: Streamed response

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 3: KV Cache Event Tracking
    vLLMZMQ->>EPP: KV cache block stored/evicted events<br/>ZMQ PUB/SUB 5556/TCP (no encryption)
    Note over EPP: Update KV Cache Index<br/>(prefix matching for scorer plugin)
